Upgrade procedure for file(1) / libmagic

Source: https://astron.com/pub/file/file-VERSION.tar.gz
        (see https://www.darwinsys.com/file/ for release announcements)

To upgrade to a new version:

1. Download and extract the new tarball to /tmp/file/file-VERSION
2. Use the vendor-update skill (vendor/file/dist, contrib/file)
3. Apply local patches after the subtree merge (see below)

Local patches applied on top of upstream:

  - FreeBSD f0ca30b4e500: file: Parse some UFS2 flags
    Adds recognition of FS_DOSOFTDEP, FS_SUJ, FS_GJOURNAL, FS_ACLS,
    FS_NFS4ACLS flags in UFS2 superblocks.
    File: magic/Magdir/filesystems (after "minimum percentage of free
    blocks" line in the ffsv2 named section)
    Accepted upstream as 482259e5e952 (will be in file 5.47+).

Notes:
  - The Xlist (MIDNIGHTBSD-Xlist) excludes test data, Windows build
    files, and Python bindings not needed on MidnightBSD.
  - Check FreeBSD's contrib/file/ git log for any new local patches
    after each upstream import.
